text: @Test void loadCoursesExistingFileCorrectFormat() f String fileName = "input\\courses.csv"; Executable e = () -> f Course.loadCourses(fileName); ); Assertions.assertDoesNotThrow(e); ) @Test void loadCoursesNonExistingFile() { String fileName = "input\\nonExistingFile.txt"; Executable e = () -> { Course.loadCourses(fileName); }; Assertions.assertThrows(java.io.FileNotFoundException.class, e); )
